        {
          "accountName": "PT_262__bgeoo_0903_b",
          "segments": [
            { "type": "PHONE_CALL_LEAD", "percent": 32.4 },
            { "type": "DOWNLOAD", "percent": 18.7 },
            { "type": "PURCHASE", "percent": 48.9 }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "apiSuggestion": {
    "method": "GET",
    "path": "/ugc/conversion/data",
    "queryParams": [
      "dateRangeStart",
      "dateRangeEnd",
      "platform",
      "appPackage|app",
      "source|adPlatform",
      "conversionType"
    ],
    "notes": [
      "如使用 querystring：建议将 dateRange 拆为 dateRangeStart/dateRangeEnd，避免数组传参差异；或改为 POST JSON body。",
      "页面会每 30s 刷新：建议接口支持缓存或增量计算，避免高频全量聚合压力。",
      "tree 表格层级固定 3 层；若后端返回更多层级，前端当前展示不支持。"
    ]
  }
}
